    "Regarding problem scale, Pan et al. [53], Sun and Yang [60], and Fu et al.",
    "[68] achieved favorable outcomes on randomly generated TSP10000 instances, while Xin et al. [71] achieved excellent results on randomly generated TSP5000 instances.",
    "In contrast, Luo et al. [55], Ma et al.",
    "[57], Ouyang et al. [59], and Liu et al.",
    "[73] attained satisfactory outcomes on randomly generated TSP1000 instances."
  ],
